645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15610,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/ramadan-umrah-hajj\/","url_meta":{"origin":38371,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: &#8216;Umrah in Ramadan equal to Hajj","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the 'Umrah pilgrimage during Ramadan is equal to Hajj.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1782, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1256 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15618,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/reward-children-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38371,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Taking children to the pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A woman lifted up her child and said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is the Hajj pilgrimage for this child?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYes, you will have a reward.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1336 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/12\/death-during-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38371,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Reward for those who die during pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever goes out for the Hajj pilgrimage and dies, the reward of Hajj will be written for him until the Day of Resurrection. Whoever goes out for the Umrah pilgrimage and dies, the reward of Umrah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38371","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminae